tafsir[89]{c,v,t}:
  43,1,"Haa, Miim. Yewtere fii sugu …óee kalfe yawtiino ka cortewol Al baqarah."
  43,2,"Allah woondirii Deftere …ìannginnde laawol peewal ngol."
  43,3,"Men wa…óii nde janngeteende e haala aarabu, no taskoron maanaaji mayre, onon …ìee …ìe nde jippinaa e haala mun, faamon …óum, egganon mofte goo."
  43,4,"Pellet, ndee Alqur'aanaare, hino ka Alluwal reenaangal, toowunde darja, √±e√±aande e yamirooje e ha…óaa…ói Aayeeje mun."
  43,5,"E Men acciray jippinirgol Alqur'aana e mon, …óuurnoragol on, fii ko fantinir…óon kon sirku e geddi? Men wa…óataa …óum ! Tawde Me…óen yurmaa on."
  43,6,"∆äuu…óii e Annabaa…ìe …ìe Min nuli e mofte adinoo…ìe …ìen."
  43,7,"Annabaajo Allah araano e …óen mofte adinoo…ìe, si wanaa …ìe wonuno e jalkitugol mo."
  43,8,"Men halkiino ko …ìuri …óen mofte sa…ótude jawlagol. Wanaa mofte …ìur…óe …ìen …óon jaasude Men ronkata fii mun ! Toode mise halkanoo…ìe goo, yawtiino ka Alqur'aana; wano Aadi'en, e Samuuda'en, e yim…ìe Luutu …ìen, e wondii…ìe Madyana …ìen."
  43,9,"Ko pellet, si an Nulaa…óo a lamndike …ìee sirkoo…ìe fennu…ìe: wiide ko hommbo tagi kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin? ∆Åe wi'ay: ko Foolu…óo Mo fooletaake On, Anndu…óo kala huunde On tagi …ói."
  43,10,"Allah wa…óiran…óo On leydi ndin weertaandi, ka rewnoton teppe mon, O wa…óani on kadi laawi e pelle e na…óf mayri, fii no …óoworon …óe ka yahdu mon."
  43,11,"On jippinir…óo ndiyam ka kammu, yeru ko yonata on onon e neemora…ói mon e remuruuji mon. Men wuurnitiri …óam, leydi yoorundi ndi alah pu…ói. Ko non tigiri, woni ko Allah wuurnitiroyta on."
  43,12,"On tagu…óo kala nooneeji …óin: wano jemma e √±aloram, gorel e deyel ekw, O wa…óirani on e laa…óe …óen e neemoraa…ói …óin, ko wa…ó…óoron ka setagol mon: wa…ó…óo…óon laa…óe …óen ka maayo, wa…ó…óo…óon neemoraa…ói …óin ka njorndi."
  43,13,"On eltiranii on …óum fow, fii yo on fotondir e hoore ko wa…ó…óoto…óon kon ka setagol mon, refti annditon neema Joomi mon On, tuma nde fotondir…óon e majji, wi'on ontuma: Laa…ìal e senayee woodanii eltan…óo men ndii ba…ó…óateeri, menen on, men wonaano ha…ótam…ìe e mun, si wanaano Allah eltani men."
  43,14,"Menen on, ko ka Joomi amen tun, woni ko men ruttoytoo, si men maayii, fii √±aaweede warjee."
  43,15,"Sirkoo…ìe …ìen aa∆¥ii wonnde tagaa…ìe goo, ko jibinaa…ìe tagu…óo On senii…óo, tuma …ìe wi'unoo: Malaa'ika'en, ko …ìi…ó…ìe Allah rew…ìe ! Pellet, ne…ó…óanke wi'oowo sugu ngol konngol, ko yeddu…óo …ìanngu…óo keeferaaku e majjere."
  43,16,"Kaa hara onon …ìee sirkoo…ìe, on wi'u wonnde Allah jogitanike hoore Makko …ìi…ó…ìe rew…ìe, e ko O tagi kon, O heertinani on onon, …ìi…ó…ìe wor…ìe …ìen? Ko hon…óum e senndoore woni kon ko aa∆¥i…óon?"
  43,17,"Si go…ó…óo e ma…ì…ìe wewliniraama jibinaneede …ìi…ó…óo debbo ko o dammbunoo kon e Joomi makko, yeeso makko ngon ni…ì…ìitira suno, metteendi ndi o wonndi. Ko honno non o dammbirta e Joomi makko, kon ko tikkinta mo, si o humpitiraama …óum."
  43,18,"E ko on ne'etee…óo e cu…óaari, hara kanko on ka yeddondiral, o …ìannginirtaa haala, sabu ndewaagu makko ngun?"
  43,19,"∆Åe inni Malaa'ika…ìe taw…ìe …ìen ko jeyaa…ìe Jom Hinaranke On, rew…ìe. Kere …ìe seedino fewndo Allah tagate …ìen, haa fee√±ani …ìe wonnde ko …ìe rew…ìe? Awa fii ngol seedagol ma…ì…ìe winndete, …ìe lamnditoyee fii mun, √ëalnde Darngal, …ìe leptiree nden fenaande ma…ì…ìe."
  43,20,"∆Åe wii ho…ìe hujjaniro koddoruyee, …ìe wi'i: si Allah haajuno, men rewataano Malaa'ika'en. Tawde O haajii …óum, hollii Himo welaa. Kono …ìe alanaa e kon ko …ìe wowlata, hay e ganndal; …ìee wonaali, si wanaa e fenugol."
  43,21,"Kaa ko Deftere Men addani …ìee sirkoo…ìe, ado Alqur'aana, daginanaynde …ìe rewugol ko woori Allah, hara ko e nden Deftere woni ko …ìe dallinorta?"
  43,22,"Ko woni kon, …ìe dallinor finaa-tawaa wiide: memen men tawu baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen e hoore diina, rewaynoo…ìe sanamu; haray ko e …óin batteeji …óon men rewata e mun."
  43,23,"Ko wano …ìee …óoo fenniri non, …ìe dallinori baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, ko non woniri Men nulaali jertinoowo yim…ìe mun aditaade ma an Nulaa…óo, si wanaa hooree…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen wi'ay: menen men tawu baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen e dow diina, …óum non ko batteeji ma…ì…ìe …óin men jokkata. Haray wanaa e maa woni ko adii e …óum."
  43,24,"Nulaa…óo ma…ì…ìe on maakani …ìe: on jokkay tun baabiraa…ìe mon …ìen, hay si mi addanii on ko …ìuri diina ma…ì…ìe kan mo∆¥∆¥ude? ∆Åe wi'i: memen dey, ko men yeddu…ìe ko nulida…óon e mun kon."
  43,25,"Men yottii e …óen mofte fennunoo…ìe Nulaa…ìe mun …ìen ado maa, Men halki …ìe. Taskii no battane ma…ì…ìe wa'unoo. Ko battane muusunoo…óe wonunoo."
  43,26,"Janto kadi yo Nulaa…óo, tuma nde Ibraahiima maakannoo ben makko e yime makko …ìen: min on ko mi da…óndii…óo e sanamuuji …ói rewoton …óin, gaanin Allah."
  43,27,"Si wanaa Allah tagu…óo lam On, On …óon fewnay lam e jokkugol diina focciika kan."
  43,28,"O wa…ói konngol tawhiidi ngol Ibraahiima maaki ngol, heddotoongol e …ìaawo makko, ngol mulataa e geyngol wootin…óinoo…ìe Allah …ìen …ìe kafidataa Mo e huunde. Belajo'o, …ìe ruttoray e Allah, tuubugol e sirku e geddi."
  43,29,"Mi hawjaano halkugol …ìee sirkoo…ìe fennu…ìe, Mi dakmitirno …ìe e heddagol e aduna, kam…ìe e baabiraa…ìe ma…ì…ìe …ìen, haa nde Alqur'aana arunoo e ma…ì…ìe, e Nulaa…óo …ìanngu…óo, woni Muhammadu (Jom kisiyee)."
  43,30,"Nde Alqur'aanaare nden ardirunoo…ìe goonga mo sikke alaa e mu'un, …ìe wi': …óum ko ko Muhammadu woni mbil…óoraade men, menen non, ko men yeddu…ìe …óum."
  43,31,"Sirkoo…ìe fennu…ìe …ìen wi'i: ko hanno Allah jippinira Alqur'aana e gooto e wor…ìe koohoo…ìe Makka maa Taa'ifu …ìen? hara wanaa e Muhammadu baaso alyatimaajo oo?"
  43,32,"E ko kam…ìe senndata yurmeende Joomi maa nden, an Nulaa…óo, sakko wona …ìe okkay nde mo …ìe yi…óani, …ìe …óala nde mo …ìe haaji, kaa ko Allah? Awa ko Menen woni ko senndi arsikeeji ma…ì…ìe …óin hakkunde ma…ì…ìe aduna, Men wa…ói e ma…ì…ìe al…óu…ìe e waasu…ìe, fii no yga ma…ì…ìe wonira eltanaa…ìe …ìeya. Haray, ko ko Joomi maa yurmetee jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen kon ka laakara, …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude e dii ko …ìee moo…ìata e aduna lannoowo on."
  43,33,"Si wanaa fii wata yim…ìe …ìen wonu e mofte goote ka keeferaaku, Men wa…óayno e cuu…ói yeddu…ìe Allah …ìen: ki…ì…ìale kaalisi, e ≈ãabbir…óe ka …ìe ∆¥awra."
  43,34,"Men wa…óayno kadi e cuu…ói ma…ì…ìe …óin, dame e dan…óe e nda…ó…óu…óe ka …ìe so…ì…ìindoo fii no …ìe unura e fitina on see…óa-see…óa."
  43,35,"Men wa…óanayno …ìe kadi cu…óaari ka≈ã≈ãe. Kono …óum fow wonaali, si wanaa ko dakamme nguurndam aduna; nafa mun ko see…óa mo juutataa. Ko neema laakara on ka Joomi maa an Nulaa…óo, …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥annde …óoftii…ìe Allah …ìen, …ìe wo…ó…óitii e ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin."
  43,36,"Kala …óuurnii…óo e Alqur'aana, haa o ronki taskagol nde, haray o leptirte wuurteede e setaneeru ndu o seertataa e mun, ko …ìeyda mo bewre."
  43,37,"∆äin awaseeji coowodaa…ói non e …ìen …óuunii…ìe Alqur'aana, ko sakkotoo…ói …ìe e diina Allah kan, haa …ìe ronka …óoftaade Mo, …ìe ha…óitoo e ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin, hara hi…ìe sikka ko …ìe feewu…ìe e goonga, …ìe ronka tuubude e nden majjere ma…ì…ìe."
  43,38,"Haa si on …óuurninoo…óo jantoore Allah nden aroyii √ëalnde Darngal, o yelora wiide: ee bone ! hara hakkunde am e maa, an oo coowodaa…óo, wo…ó…óirayno go…ó…óal fu…ónaange e hiirnaange wo…ó…óondiri ! Tawde a bonii coowodaa…óo !"
  43,39,"Allah daalana heefer…ìe …ìen nden √ëalnde: …óum nafataa on hannde - nde tawnoo on too√±iriino ko'e-mon sirku e geddi - wonnde on hawtoyte ka lepte. ∆Åe sirkan…óon …ìe, ronnditantaako on huunde e lepte …óen."
  43,40,"∆Åee ko faa…óu…ìe e nanugol goonga, wumi…óu…ìe e yi'ugol mo. Hara non ko an Nulaa…óo, woni ko waawata naninnde faa…óu…óo maa fewna bun…óo maa majju…óo laawol focciingol ngol?"
  43,41,"Si Men aru ∆¥ettitude ma ado Men leptude …ìe, haray doo ko Men yottoray…ìe e ma…ì…ìe, leptugol aduna e laakara."
  43,42,"Maa hara Men holle yoga e ko lepte …óe Men kammbirani …ìe …óen, haray doo ko Men gaynoo…ìe fii ma…ì…ìe. ∆Åe ha…ótanaa dartagol Men e huunde."
  43,43,"An Nulaa…óo, jogito kon ko Joomi maa wahayini e maa…óa, golitiraa …óum. Pellet, hi…óa jokki laawol goonga, ngol jil…ìuya alah e mum."
  43,44,"Ndee Alqur'aanaare non, ko teddungal maa…óa an e yim…ìe maa. Arma nde lamndite…óon fii gom…óingol nde ngol, e rewgol peewal hende ngal, e noddugol e mayre ngol √ëalnde Darngal."
  43,45,"An Nulaao, lamndii e …ìen …ìe Nulunoo ado maa, si tawii Men wa…óuno tanaa Allaahu On, rewetee…ói goo?"
  43,46,"Gom…óii Men immindinii Muusaa e Aayeeje Amen …óen, haa e Fir'awna e mbatu yim…ìe makko …ìen, o maakani …ìe: ko mi Nulaa…óo Jey…óo tageefo ngon fow."
  43,47,"Nde o addannoo…ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen, …ìe woni e jalugol …óe jalkita."
  43,48,"Men hollaali Fir'awna e mbatu mun ngun hujja semmbin…óo ko Muusaa addi kon, si wanaa haray ko on …ìuri adii…óo mo on mawnude. Men nanngiri …ìe lepte …óen aduna, jortagol nde …ìe …ìoorotoo e keeferaaku, kono …óum nafaano."
  43,49,"Nde memi …ìe huunde e lepte, …ìe wi'ani Muusaa (yo o his): ko an yo mbileejo! Torano men Joomi maa, ko O jantimaa kon ka fii huncugol lepte …óen, si wonii men gom…óinii. Tawde pellet, ko men feewoo…ìe, si O huncanii men lepte …óen."
  43,50,"Nde Men huncannoo…ìe lepte …óen, e jaka yoo, hi…ìe firta ahadi ma…ì…ìe ndin."
  43,51,"Fir'awna noddi e yim…ìe makko …ìen, o woni e mantorgol laamu makko ngun, wi'angol …ìe: ko onon yo yim…ìe am, wanaa min jey laamu Misra? E hino …óii can…ói Niilu ngol hino ila e ley ku…ìeeje am? E on yi*aani laamu am ngun, haa anndon mawngu am ngun?"
  43,52,"Ko min …ìuri teddungal, e dii Muusaa lo'u…óo, on mo lobbintaa haala."
  43,53,"Awa ko hanno Allah werloo jawe ka≈ã≈ãe, e oo mo O nuli, no o hollira wonnde ko o Nulaa…óo Makko? Maa…óum Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen arda e makko nun, hara ko …ìe jokkondir…ìe?"
  43,54,"Fir'awna …óaytini …óaytini yim…ìe makko …ìen, …ìe …óoftii majjere makko nden. Pellet, …ìen …óon laatino yim…ìe yaltu…ìe e …óoftaare Allah."
  43,55,"Nde …ìe tikkinirnoo Men ha…ì…ìitagol e keeferaaku ngun, Men yottii e ma…ì…ìe; Men yooli …ìe fow ma…ì…ìe."
  43,56,"Men wa…ói Fir'awna e yim…ìe mun …ìen, adii…ìe yim…ìe …ìen e keeferaaku, Men wa…óti …ìe waajitortee…ìe, wonannde kala waajitorii…óo …ìe, fii wata sugu mun he…ìu …óum."
  43,57,"Nde sirkoo…ìe …ìen sikkunoo wonnde Iisaa, Mo Annasaara'en rewata on, hino jeyaa e …ìe Allah daali fii mun …ìen :""Pellet, onon e ko rewoton kon gaanin Allah, ko on carmalle Jahannama. Ko on joloyay…ìe e magge"", e hino le Allah ha…óii rewugol mo, no O ha…óiri rewugol sanamuuji …óin non, tawaa yoo, yim…ìe maa …ìen, an Nulaa…óo, hino sonka wennjondiree, …ìe wi'i: men weltorii tawde rewetee…óo amen on, ko martaba Iisaa woni. Allah jippini …óon kisan, ko raddira …ìe: ""Pellet, …ìen …ìe mo∆¥∆¥i …óin adanii …óum ka Amen, …ìen …óon ko wo…ó…óintintee…ìe e magge"""
  43,58,"∆Åe wi'i: Ko rewetee…ói amen …óin …ìuri mo∆¥∆¥ude, kaa ko iisaa? Ibn az-Ziba‚Äôraa e nanndo makko piyiranaali ngal misal, fii he…ìugol yottaade ka, ko fii tun wennjodnireede. ∆Åen ko yim…ìe sa…ótu…ìe wennje."
  43,59,"Iisaa ge…óal Maryama on wonaali, si wanaa jeyaa…óo Allah, mo Men neeminiri Annabaaku e Nuleede, Men wa…ói mo misal wonannde …ìi…ó…ìe Israa'iila …ìen, ko …ìe dallinora e kattal Allah ngal, nde tawnoo O tagirmo ko aldaa e baaba, wano O tagiri Aadama ko aldaa e jibim…ìe."
  43,60,"Si Men haajuno gaynugol fii mon, onon …ìi…ó…ìe Aadama …ìen, Men wa…óirayno …óum, wa…ótitirgol on Malaa'ika, ko lomtoo on ka leydi, …ìe wona e rewugol Allah, hara …ìe kafidataa Mo e go…ó…óum."
  43,61,"Ko pellet, Iisaa ko maande jeyaande e maandeeji Darngal maw…ói …óin, tuma o jippoytoo ka jamaanu sakkitoru. Wata on sikkito fii …óum. Jokkee lam e ko mi addi kon immorde ka Allah, ko …óum woni laawol focciingol ngol."
  43,62,"Wata seytaane falor on e laawol focciingol ngol, …óayne e koomte maako …óen ! tawde pellet, ko o ga√±o mon …ìanngin…óo ngayngu."
  43,63,"Nde Iisaa (jom kisiyee) on ardannoo yim…ìe makko …ìen hujjaaji …ìanngin…ói Nulala makko ngal, o maakani …ìe: Gom…óii mi ardanii on e √±ee√±al immorde ka Allah, e no …ìannginirana on yoga e ko luutondir…óon e mun, ka diina mon. Haray huliree Allah, …óoftagol yamiraa…ói Makko …óin, e wo…ó…óitagol ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin. ∆äofton mi e ko yamirta on kon, rento…óon e ko mi ha…ói on e mun kon."
  43,64,"Pellet, ko Allah woni Joomi am e Joomi mon. Rewetee…óo goo alanaa en. La…ì…ìinanee mo Kanko tun, dewe …óen. Ko …óum woni laawol focciingol ngol."
  43,65,"Feddeeji Annasaara …óin luutondiri hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, fii Iisaa: wo…ó…ìe wi'i: ko o rewetee…óo, wo…ó…ìe …ìen wi'i: ko o …ìi…ó…óo Allah, wo…ó…ìe goo wi'i: kanko fow e neene makko, ko …ìe rewetee…ìe. Awa bone woodanii …ìen too√±ir…ìe ko'e mun, siforgol Iisaa rewetee…óo, maa …ìi…ó…óo maa tammo tammitaa…ìe, immorde e lepte muusu…óe, habbitii…óe …ìe √ëalnde Darngal."
  43,66,"Hara …óii feddeejii luutondir…ói fii Iisaa no habbii si wanaa nde Darngal ngal ardata …ìe e juhal, hara …ìe so'aa anndude fii …óum? Si ngal arii …ìe e fewndo keeferaaku ma…ì…ìe, haray battane ma…ì…ìe, ko lepte muusu…óe."
  43,67,"Weldun…ìe yi…óindiri …ìen e majjere keeferaaku, yoga ma…ì…ìe ayroyay yoga, √ëalnde Darngal; si wanaa hulir…ìe Allah …ìen, …óoftagol yamaruyeeji Makko …óin, wo…ó…óitoo e ha…óaa…ói Makko …óin. ∆Åen …óon, weldigal ma…ì…ìe ngal duumoto."
  43,68,"Allah daalano …ìen gom…óum…ìe: Ko onon yo jeyaa…ìe Am ! Kulol alanaa on hannde, e fii ko yawtiri on kon; wanaa on sunoray…ìe kadi, fii ge…ìoy aduna yawtukoy."
  43,69,"∆Åen gom…óim…ìe Alqur'aanaare jippiinde nden e Nulaa…óo ma…ì…ìe on, …ìe woni jebbilanii…ìe nde; waajitoray …ìe, …ìe ha…óitora ka…óaa…ói mayre kadi."
  43,70,"Naatee ka Aljanna, onon e nanndu…ìe e mon gom…óinal, hara hi…óon weltora neemaaji duumotoo…ói, …ói lannataa, ta∆¥ondirtaa."
  43,71,"Golloo…ìe hino wanngindinee e ma…ì…ìe, miranji ka≈ã≈ãe e √±eddu…óe yoo…óu…óe. Hino ka Aljanna ton: kala ko wonkii muuyetee, gite dakmitora ndaarugol. Hara non, ko on duumotoo…ìe ton, on yaltatah haa poomaa."
  43,72,"Ko on Aljanna mo sifana…óon fii mun, woni mo Allah roniniri on …ìural Makko, sabu kon ko gollayno…óon."
  43,73,"Hino woodani on ton, muuyantee…ói …óuu…óu…ói, …ói ta∆¥ondirtaa, ko e …óin √±aamoton."
  43,74,"Pellet, bonnir…ìe keeferaaku e geddi …ìen, ko ka lepte Janhannama …ìe luttoyta √ëalnde Darngal, …ìe heddoo ton poomaa."
  43,75,"∆Åe hoynantaake lepte …óen, wurin hara ko …ìe ta∆¥ii…ìe e yurmeende Allah nden."
  43,76,"Men too√±iraali …ìe naadugol …ìe Yiite, si ko woni, ko kam…ìe too√±irnoo ko'e ma…ì…ìe keeferaaku."
  43,77,"∆Åe nodda Malaa'ikaajo halfinaa…óo Yiite ngen on, …ìe wi'a: ko an yo Maaliku ! Yo Joomi maa gaynu fii amen, men foofto e lepte …óen. O jaabitoo …ìe: pellet, ko e …óen lepte luttoton poomaa, on maayataa ton, sakko lepte …óen ta∆¥ondira e mon."
  43,78,"Gom…óii Men addanno on goonga ka sikke alaa e mu'un ; kono …óuu…óu…ìe e mon, ko a√±unoo…ìe goonga."
  43,79,"Si …ìe fewjanii Annabiijo on (yo o his), haray doo ko Men fewjanoo…ìe …ìe feere …ìurnde nden …óon."
  43,80,"Kaa hara …ìe sikku wonnde Men nanataa gunndooji ma…ì…ìe …óin e sirruuji ma…ì…ìe …óin? Ko pellet, Men nanay …ói fow ! Wuri Malaa'ikaa…ìe …ìen hino maandina kala ko …ìe huuwi."
  43,81,"An Nulaa…óo, maakan dammbu…ìe …ìi…ó…ìe rew…ìe …ìen e Allah: wonnde O siforaali jogitagol …ìi…ó…óo ! O laa…ìii O senike e …óum ! Si …óum wonuno, ko min woni adii…óo rewude Alla cenii…óo O."
  43,82,"Senyanee woodanii Jey…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, Jey…óo kadi Arsi kin e kon ko …ìee sirkoo…ìe dammbirta Mo debbo e …ìi…ó…óo."
  43,83,"Nulaa…óo, accu…ìe …ìe jumpa e meere nde …ìe woni e mun, …ìe fija haa …ìe hawroya e √±alaande ma…ì…ìe nde …ìe fodaa, ndeen woni √ëalnde Darngal."
  43,84,"Ko Kanko Allah woni rewetee…óo e goonga On ka kammu e ka leydi, ko Kanko kadi woni √ëee√±o e tagu Mun e e…ì…ìoore Mun e toppitagol Mun, Anndu…óo fiyakuuji jeyaa…ìe Makko …ìen. Mo tawata huunde suu…óaaki Mo e fii ma…ì…ìe."
  43,85,"Mo∆¥∆¥ere Allah e barki Makko …ìeydanike Mo, Kanko On Mo woodani …óum laamu kammuuli …óin e leyd ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji. Ko ka Makko tun, anndal fii daragol Darngal woni, go…ó…óo goo anndaa …óum. Ko ka Makko tun kadi, woni ruttorde mon laakara, fii √±aaweede yo…ìitee."
  43,86,"∆äi sirkoo…ìe …ìen rewata …óin acca Allah, …ói waawataa tefoygol ka Allah, si wanaa …ìen seedii…ìe konngol liimaanu ngol, hara hi…ìe anndi ko …ìe seedii kon: wano Iisaa, e‚ÄòUzayru, e Malaa'ika'en."
  43,87,"Ko pellet, si a lamndike …ìe, ko hommbo woni ko tagi …ìe? ∆Åe wi'ete: Ko Allah. Ko honno non …ìe yiiliraa e rewugol Mo, …ìaawo …ìe qirritaade …óum?"
